<Layout title="Foreign Residents Selling Brisbane Property: CGT Withholding Explained | Daniel Gierach Property" description="Foreign residents selling Australian property face ATO withholding on the purchase price. Here is what the regime covers, who it affects, and what sellers need to do before listing." draft={draft}>

<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
